      "description": "## Code Review Fixes\n\n- Remove generic 'General' heading from settings tab\n- Fix API compatibility: revert setDestructive() (not in stable API) to setWarning()\n- Fix floating promise in extract-section toolbar button\n- Remove unused SeparatorStyle import\n- Fix authorUrl reachability (trailing slash)",
