      "author": "gurjar1",
      "description": "## Fixes\n\n- **Section strip breadcrumb/nav toggle**: The hide-breadcrumb and hide-nav-arrows settings were broken in 1.5.2 due to \toggleClass being used without a matching CSS rule. Fixed by adding a general .ah-strip-hidden { display: none } rule.\n- **Style consistency**: Replaced remaining style.display assignments in the section strip with \toggleClass, consistent with the Obsidian review compliance changes in v1.5.2.\n- Minor whitespace cleanup in command registry.",
