      "author": "gurjar1",
      "description": "## Bug Fixes\n- Fix heading numbers restarting after code blocks containing ~~~ (e.g. Python tracebacks with ~~~^~). Root cause: non-CommonMark-compliant fence detection incorrectly treating content lines as code fence delimiters.\n\n## Obsidian Review Compliance (61 issues resolved)\n- Replace all inline style assignments with CSS classes\n- Use window.setTimeout/clearTimeout/requestAnimationFrame for popout window compatibility\n- Fix all floating promises with \u000boid operator\n- Replace \require() imports with static imports\n- Remove unnecessary type assertions and eslint-disable directives\n- Fix unsafe \u0007ny member access with proper typing\n- Remove unused imports\n- Remove plugin name from settings heading\n- Replace deprecated setWarning() API",
