      "author": "gurjar1",
      "description": "## Bug Fixes\n- Fix cursor jumping to start of heading during typing\n- Fix auto-number delay setting being ignored (was hardcoded to 2s)\n- Fix toolbar buttons using stale line state after typing\n- Fix heading numbering instability after burn-in\n\n## Other Improvements\n- Initialize settings snapshot on file-open\n- Cancel pending burn-in timer on file switch and plugin unload\n- Sync package-lock.json version",
